v2026.05.31.11 — Install preview Show Details button fix + Finish layout + cleanup

dialogs.h / dialogs.cpp — Show Details button (IDC_IDLG_INSTALL_PRV_DET_BTN=7146):
  Was IDC=0 so WM_DRAWITEM never routed to DrawCustomButton — grey box. Fixed:
  proper IDC assigned, WM_DRAWITEM guard extended, WM_COMMAND click calls
  ShowValidationDialog with preview notice (idlg_install_prv_det_preview).

dialogs.cpp — Select Folder preview allow-change fix (icon-only rule):
  EnableWindow(hBrowse, FALSE) removed per button_INTERNALS: icon-only buttons
  must not be disabled — no ODS_DISABLED path in DrawCustomButton.
  Only hPathEdit is disabled when !s_selectFolderAllowChange.

dialogs.cpp — LayoutPreviewControls split-layout content height cap:
  contentH was capped at min(S(contentFitH), avail) — could fill 100% of
  available height, pushing extras panel off-screen. Now capped at
  avail - gap - extrasNaturalH (floor S(40)). Fixes Finish page: logo fully
  visible with launch checkbox below it.

dialogs.cpp — ShowFinishFeedback removed (~150 lines):
  FinishFeedbackWndProc, FinishFbData, IDC_FFBK_* and ShowFinishFeedback
  body deleted. The Finish page preview already shows the launch checkbox;
  a second Installation Complete dialog was redundant.
